attributes.action: Seek to ensure access to clean water for the people of Palestine
attributes.additional_details: To prevent Palestinians from dying of dehydration and suffering ill effects of drinking unclean water.
attributes.background: We want the Government to take whatever action is necessary to ensure the people of Palestine can access clean water. This should include diplomatic pressure on Israel.
